{"type": "article", "id": 30169, "title": "以日本曲木为灵感设计的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-26T23:02:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160726211524TIDMvktZcey4d6uo.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>我们曾经介绍过印度工作室 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saif Faisal</a> 推出的一款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29629.html\">灯具</a>，他们的新作 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/counterpoise-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Counterpoise</a> 台灯同样具有能够随意进行调节的特点。这款灯具的设计灵感来源于日本一种被称为 Magewappa 的曲木工艺，木制的圆形灯罩带给人一种自然温暖的感觉。黑色的灯柱将灯罩与光滑的底座连接在一起，并没有额外采用五金零件，使整体造型显得十分流畅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726212742lU1iWjonhYdNFmyS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.806667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726212742tXGFAfeKuJjEp4qQ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726212742Rdf85IkjL4cgNiMo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.376667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726212742O5v4CWQXaFzkdY8g.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.251135\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}